window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Only one thing keeps me from turning this world into a nightmare...and that's the angel of a woman I've fallen in love with.</b></p> <p>Her purity and beauty are the only things that soothe my tortured soul.</p> <p>The world fears me. It doesn't matter if you're a human, orc, or dark elf—you shrink away in terror when I come into view.</p> <p>Only Moira can keep me at bay.</p> <p>I'll kill anyone or anything that tries to harm her. I'll rip them apart as they still breathe and feed them pieces of themselves with dark delight.</p> <p>That's nothing compared to what I'll do to her if she tries to leave me. She's mine. Forever.</p> <p>Together, we will rule the land of nightmares. She by my side.</p> <p>Whether she likes it or not.</p>"; 
